des: Dry Cleaning and Laundry becomes easier with pickup and delivery dry cleaning and laundry services. Just say 'Alexa, open The Plaza Cleaners' to get started! Now you can tell The Plaza Cleaners you are on your way so they can have your clothes ready by the time you get there! Just say, 'Alexa, tell The Plaza Cleaners I am on my way' to let The Plaza Cleaners know you are on your way!
